&lt;p&gt;We have shifts available at our COVID-19 Hub in Harrow from November 16th onwards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The COVID-19 Hub is based at Alexandra Avenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The shifts are 8-2pm or 2-8pm and take place 7 days a week. Rates are £37 for Nurses/ANPs, £22 for HCAs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will undertaking patient swabs, and ensuring infection control at the centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally you work within NWL London and have dealt with COVID-19 infection control processes in other place of work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be in a low-risk group for COVID-19.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please see the SOP for information about the service required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please attach your CV and advise of your availability in your application.&lt;/p&gt;
